    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253980/extras/23b8e53c9f32a776166a40c6df00d483.poster.avif?t=1771793098\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253980/extras/23b8e53c9f32a776166a40c6df00d483.webm?t=1771793098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253980/extras/23b8e53c9f32a776166a40c6df00d483.mp4?t=1771793098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Net 24h — a chaotic Vietnamese internet cafe simulator.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you don’t just manage computers.<br>You survive the madness of running a 24/7 cybercafe in Vietnam, where anything can happen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Angry customers, broken machines, unexpected police raids, and nonstop drama are part of daily life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253980/extras/8850434762ff28fe311f99db36c1686a.poster.avif?t=1771793098\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253980/extras/8850434762ff28fe311f99db36c1686a.webm?t=1771793098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253980/extras/8850434762ff28fe311f99db36c1686a.mp4?t=1771793098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage and expand your own Vietnamese internet cafe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy PCs, consoles, snacks, and upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deal with unpredictable customers and chaotic events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive stressful nights full of hilarious disasters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a Vietnam-inspired setting rarely seen in games</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Net 24h is not a peaceful simulator.<br>It is a comedy survival experience inspired by real internet cafe culture in Vietnam.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you keep the shop running, or will the chaos consume you?</p>",
